{"tid":1228594,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[求安慰］發夢呃咗全家冇去示威 好對唔住佢哋","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T17:55:08.000Z","uid":192306,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1ca410c684764160fedede3df782d1c7240047","tid":1228594,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"Sor篇嘢好長但係俾我呻吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發夢住喺學校宿舍所以星期三去咗金鐘都冇人知。嗰日全家係咁問我喺邊，有冇去金鐘，咁唔想屋企人擔心加上有藍底家人嘅我梗係呃佢哋話冇啦<br />\n<br />\n但係咁樣呃屋企人我真係好内疚，好對唔住佢哋。其實比起政見佢哋一定更關心我人身安全。明明自己食緊彈，隨時俾狗拉，佢哋仲咩都唔知，以為自己個女，孫女安全。<br />\n<br />\n最諷刺係俾呀公讚我唔似其他同學咁傻衝出去，同屋企人憶述啲經歷都要加翻句「我朋友」，見到佢哋放下心頭大石嘅樣，仲要呃佢哋講「傻啦點會出去呀咁危險」，我真係覺得自己好差，咁呃屋企人真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過真係情願呃佢哋都會繼續出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比起呃屋企人我會更加內疚冇出嚟"},{"pid":"8e3de314c6f2b5d1d3a6a692cb21ffe79a497bdb","tid":1228594,"uid":222568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:29:46.000Z","msg":"加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fd2790cc90a76a8f8cc15d859b03fbb8fb6104","tid":1228594,"uid":208931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"情況一模一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢記得小心啲就得<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"e8e31448a02b543e38db37832c4450eab82a7e66","tid":1228594,"uid":9480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:31:58.000Z","msg":"加油樓主"},{"pid":"90a2b1b96c59d030b5dafb6cd0d8a78567589ded","tid":1228594,"uid":73089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"拎你屋企人出嚟祭旗啦"},{"pid":"2276753afdddabe5335e2ebb9bf383501f924f63","tid":1228594,"uid":192306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a2b1b96c59d030b5dafb6cd0d8a78567589ded","tid":1228594,"uid":73089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTi